metadata.name: EARLY SPRING BIRD
metadata.description:
You notice very quickly when it's spring again. The birds chirp much louder. In the morning there is still a fine damp dew. As if from nowhere the first flowers appear. The sun reflects in the moist air. Many little animals crawl out of their holes. A wonderful stage of nature. Spring is a wonderful gift every year.

Artist: Kathrin Federer
Created 2021 in Photoshop
3030 x 3787 px | 300 dpi
Edition 1/1
